snippet.title: Amber Heard thinks she is a Rabbit?!?! Food abuse PART 2.
snippet.description:
#JusticeForJohnnyDepp #AmberHeard #JohnnyDepp
My good friend Ashley joined me on this journey of sarcasm and satire about Amber. We discuss how Amber wants to become a Rabbit. This video is almost entirely a joke and not meant to actually be taken seriously. I think it is obvious from the contents of the video. Let's not forget that we need to support Johnny Depp as best we can.
